91,"uid":59984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dd3893178cf4b4c5358ec27a0d4403050d2f85","tid":1594691,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"152efd66c4b72c273abb6b625cf7f7a51903880c","tid":1594691,"uid":298585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n只有脫離中共管治香港先會正常番"},{"pid":"35f07c3442daab27d2178706894563e0012d9488","tid":1594691,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"求下大家 思想唔好再停留喺相信中共會俾5大訴求你<br />\n記唔記得之前嘅袋住先？<br />\n睇下我篇文 認真咁考慮要唔要從根源解決問題<br />\n<blockquote>大家點睇脫共？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536794</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"39e9e55198d6e6ba74d728125d18d577a1613af3","tid":1594691,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07b5a28c1fdf71f67275390c70297e1422009945","tid":1594691,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:26:17.000Z","msg":"運動需要一個突破點，係一個完全嘅升級，應該提升至追求<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">終極自治</span></span>嘅層次<br />\n主權在民，新成立嘅民主政府就絕對有能力回應抗爭者嘅五大訴求，亦係根治極權欺壓人民，防止同樣事件發生嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n政府一直唔回應五大訴求，運動開始陷入膠著<br />\n如果咁樣持續落去就會令本身出嚟抗爭嘅人產生無力感，出現抗爭疲勞問題<br />\n每個禮拜出嚟遊行示威對於一個本身要返工返學嘅學位真係好辛苦<br />\n再咁樣落去，就好容易步法國黃背心後塵，場運動會慢慢瓦解<br />\n<br />\n解決唯一辦法，係嚟一次全面升級，唔係武力升級，而係目標上升級<br />\n面對強權打壓，搞革命，抗爭，係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6MVGwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6MVGwi.jpg&h=1ed93f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWKL3KV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWKL3KV.jpg&h=63206eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dGKzOZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dGKzOZ.jpg&h=bcba39e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqWCakp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqWCakp.jpg&h=6804524c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbFLjcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbFLjcd.jpg&h=70135473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【自治先有民主】Ｄｏｎａｌｄ Ｔｒｕｍｐ：「洗唔洗畫公仔畫出腸呀香港人？！」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593757</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人到了獨立建國的時候 － 五大訴求的陷阱 滅共自治才是出路<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584360</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"天琦都有咁講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXThPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=edd576a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a>"},{"pid":"4758d01ac318f132899fd8638d9d7ae9583b4435","tid":1594691,"uid":102703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"短期內冇軍火如何滅共？你可能話打經濟牌，姐係去番長期消耗戰啦，咁長期戰黎講有雙普選先的確係百利而無一害，有人咁講過（好似係白兵定細良兄），<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有左真雙普選之後點樣擺脫你上面講既中共既利益操控/種票/掌心雷/偽素人實質建制底等等將會係港人自治既課題/考試</span></strong></span>，我地過到之後，就有本錢建立自己既政治經濟體系，再而有兵力，就可以有同中共談判既籌碼，好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7768eb3830dd8c9473f6db9cf674240e07718106","tid":1594691,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e1c7fd54e38dbf53165c00cf66d51c8908d031c","tid":1594691,"uid":271337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8615da4dccb65312b1a6f82b17734f7ab89db8b1","tid":1594691,"uid":298585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca1c4fdd459f39ff1913a576655c7407c2653553","tid":1594691,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"我明你嘅顧慮，但係目前黎講大部分市民個思想仲停留係港人治港，對獨立仲有啲抗拒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:37:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:05:34.000Z","msg":"唔反對獨立  但社會大眾大部份傾向雙普選  所以覺得之後運動嘅主軸可以定為爭取雙普選   <br />\n同時  主張要配合理論同計劃支持<br />\n我地要將討論雙普選方案加入日程架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"冇錯係雙普選，雖然經678月我相信多咗人唔反感獨立，但唔反感同ready又係兩件事嚟。<br />\n應該有頗多人仲停留/啱啱到喺永續基本法嗰步，雖然明明今次擺明有眼見中共唔收皮，有基本法都冇撚用。<br />\n另一樣concern就係假設今場我哋贏咗，剩低時間同環境夠唔夠我哋推獨立。"}]}